Author: garnetcoinofficial
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GARNETCOIN [GNC]
Body: GARNETCOIN  ABOUT :  Garnet is different than any currency you've used before, so it's very important to understand some key points. Unlike government issued money that can be inflated at will, the supply of Garnet is mathematically limited to 200 Million Garnet and that can never be changed.  FEATURES :  TRANSFERABLE: Garnet Coins are transferable between Rewards Programs, Participating Merchants & Banks.  COST REDUCTION: Banks will see cost reductions deploying the self-sustaining garnet coins Eco system.  TRANSPARENCY: Garnet coins are transparent by design and have a secured limited supply.  SEAMLESS: Garnet coins can be integrated seamlessly without any consumer or business disruption.  TRADABLE: Garnet coins can be bought and sold on participating crypto exchanges and added to consumers participating reward points programs.  ROADMAP :  Q3 2017 : Concept Planning & Product Design Q4 2017 : Product White Papers & Token Sale Event Q1 2018 : End Of Token Sale & Launch Of Garnet Coin & Listing On Exchanges Q1 2018 : Launch Of Mobile Wallets & Investment Portal Q2 2018 : Opening Law Offices World Wide  WEBSITE | WHITEPAPERS
